FBIS4-39146 "drsov108_b_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-108 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Rutskoy, Others To Establish `Democratic Center' Rutskoy, Others To Establish `Democratic Center' LD0406183994 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 1800 GMT 4 Jun 94 LD0406183994 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy Russian BFN [Text] Regional branches of the Democratic Party of Russia, the Party of Russian Unity and Accord, the Social Democratic Party, and the Social Democratic People's Party of Aleksandr Rutskoy are hoping to set up a united democratic center in Moscow. This issue was tackled today by the steering committee of the united center. Ilya Roytman, one of the center's organizers, said that the center will become a coordinating body, able to identify and support united democratic candidates in the run-up to the next election.
